 rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = timed out waiting for server handshake\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"17004f02-74c1-4444-9be1-b2e134544a72\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart/checkout\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"e3701923-f30f-4b62-92b0-f0e0a40b8f66\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-05T20:30:38.16210821Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-07,frontend,frontend-1,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = failed to charge card: could not charge the card: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.55.4:50051: i/o timeout\\\"\"\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"9493c2a8-63fb-460c-91c4-73803b27304c\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart/checkout\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"366859a6-2f48-493d-85f9-e2d3dec270cb\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-05T20:32:26.77861075Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["frontend-2", "frontend-1", "frontend-0"], "service_name": ["frontend"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-04", "aiops-k8s-07", "aiops-k8s-03"]}, "matched_anomaly": "Please analyze the abnormal event between 2025-06-05T20:10:09Z and 2025-06-05T20:34:09Z and provide the root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-05 20:10:09+00:00 to 2025-06-05 20:34:09+00:00"}, "log_data_collected": true, "log_analysis_findings": "基于对异常时间段 2025-06-05T20:10:09Z 到 2025-06-05T20:34:09Z 的日志分析，我发现了关键的错误模式。以下是分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"timeout\", \"i/o timeout\", \"timed out waiting for server handshake\", \"connection error\", \"transport\", \"Error while dialing\", \"context canceled\", \"Unavailable\", \"Internal\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"支付服务出现连接超时和握手超时问题，导致前端服务无法完成支付操作\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to charge card: could not charge the card: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = timed out waiting for server handshake\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"支付服务网络连接异常，出现I/O超时错误，无法建立TCP连接\",\n      \"evidence\": \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.55.4:50051: i/o timeout\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"前端服务在支付超时后出现上下文取消错误，表明请求被主动终止\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析要点总结**：\n\n1. **主要错误模式**：所有错误都来自前端服务（frontend），涉及支付流程中的支付服务调用失败\n2. **关键发现**：支付服务（paymentservice）在IP地址10.233.55.4:50051上出现严重的网络连接问题\n3. **错误类型**：\n   - 服务器握手超时（timed out waiting for server handshake）\n   - I/O超时（i/o timeout）\n   - 连接错误（connection error）\n   - 上下文取消（context canceled）\n\n4. **影响范围**：所有三个前端实例（frontend-0, frontend-1, frontend-2）都受到影响，错误持续整个异常时间段\n\n这表明支付服务可能存在网络连接问题或服务不可用，导致前端无法完成订单支付流程。", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的监控数据，我现在进行全面的初始扫描分析。以下是我的发现：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"支付服务完全不可用，错误状态显示：'connection error: dial tcp 10.233.55.4:50051: i/o timeout'，表明支付服务网络连接超时\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice内部PaymentService/Charge调用延迟从12.8秒激增至24,427秒（延迟倍数1,900倍），PlaceOrder调用延迟从145-159秒激增至22-30秒（延迟倍数150-200倍）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"前端服务出现大量HTTP 500错误，总计36+14+13=63次错误，主要原因是下游checkoutservice调用失败\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"shippingservice的GetQuote调用延迟从200ms增加至600-640ms（延迟倍数3倍），显示轻微性能影响\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"productcatalogservice的GetProduct调用延迟从9.6-10秒增加至11-19秒（延迟倍数1.1-2.0倍），显示中等性能影响\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现总结：\n\n1. **根因定位**：`paymentservice`是明确的根因服务，表现为完全的网络连接超时错误。\n\n2. **影响传播路径**：\n   - `paymentservice`不可用 → `checkoutservice`支付调用超时 → `frontend`订单处理失败 → 用户端HTTP 500错误\n\n3. **延迟特征**：\n   - 最严重的延迟在`checkoutservice->paymentservice`调用链上（1,900倍延迟增加）\n   - 整个调用链的延迟从毫秒级激增至秒级\n\n4. **错误模式**：\n   - 连接超时（i/o timeout）和上下文取消（context canceled）是主要错误类型\n   - 错误从下游向上游传播，符合根因分析原则", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的监控数据分析，我已经识别出了异常时间段内的关键指标变化。以下是初步扫描结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"rrt\", \"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"pod_cpu_usage\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max和rrt指标显著飙升，最大响应时间从199453增加到20122078.5，变化率196.07%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max: 199453.0 -> 20122078.5 (变化率1.9607), rrt: 6940.76 -> 539988.77 (变化率1.9492)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max和rrt指标异常增长，同时出现server_error_ratio和error_ratio错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max: 212274.0 -> 14046338.0 (变化率1.9405), rrt: 12244.98 -> 81378.77 (变化率1.4768), error_ratio: 0.0 -> 0.09, server_error_ratio: 0.0 -> 0.09\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max和rrt指标严重劣化，同时出现error_ratio和server_error_ratio错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max: 252690.0 -> 20126514.5 (变化率1.9504), rrt: 12344.01 -> 122931.98 (变化率1.635), error_ratio: 0.0 -> 0.19, server_error_ratio: 0.0 -> 0.19\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max和rrt指标显著恶化，出现server_error_ratio和error_ratio错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max: 248283.0 -> 20064311.0 (变化率1.9511), rrt: 12340.42 -> 116399.14 (变化率1.6166), error_ratio: 0.0 -> 0.0, server_error_ratio: 0.0 -> 0.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"出现client_error_ratio和error_ratio错误，但rrt指标有所改善\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio: 0.0 -> 0.0 (p99变化率2.0), error_ratio: 0.0 -> 0.0 (p99变化率2.0), rrt_max: 4495.0 -> 2851.5 (改善44.74%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"出现client_error_ratio和error_ratio错误，rrt_max指标有轻微变化\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio: 0.0 -> 0.0 (p99变化率2.0), error_ratio: 0.0 -> 0.0 (p99变化率2.0), rrt_max: 3899.0 -> 3350.0 (变化率15.15%)\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现：**\n1. **严重性能劣化**：checkoutservice-2和所有frontend实例的响应时间指标(rrt_max, rrt)出现10-100倍的异常增长\n2. **错误率上升**：多个服务出现错误率指标异常，特别是frontend服务的server_error_ratio\n3. **影响范围广**：故障涉及前端服务、购物车服务和结算服务，形成连锁反应\n\n**下一步建议：**\n需要进一步分析这些服务之间的调用依赖关系，以确定故障的源头和传播路径。"}
